ActCanadian Multiculturalism Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of State (Diversity and Inclusion and Youth) as the Minister for the Purposes of that Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2015-1248 of November 4, 2015; and (2) designating the Minister of State (Diversity and Inclusion and Youth), a member of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the CANADIAN MULTICULTURALISM ACT.
